  "text": "All changes with Á 2 < 0 are accepted. A change with Á 2 > 0 may be accepted with a probability of P = exp(ÀÁ 2 /2) (Proffen & Neder, 1999; [CITATION_1] ). The 2 term affects the probability of the change being accepted. If 2 = 0 then P = 0 and only changes that improve the fit, Á 2 < 0, will be accepted.",
